subject: libXi should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.
commitMessage:
libXi should not try to build into a pure wayland platform.

Tizen devel  | Tizen release
_____________|______________
succeeded    | succeeded
excluded     | excluded
broken       |
failed       |
unresolvable |
blocked      |
locked       |
note:
    - The disabled status is only
      allowed for OBS administration.
